info.description:
Heimdallr

A package for live plotting lab relevant information directly in your browser


## Demo ![demo](.github/images/demo/demo.png "demo") ## Usage - Setup MQTT broker connection information heimdallr mqtt_token - On computation machines run the publisher service. heimdallr publish - Run server service on the displaying machine. heimdallr serve
